description.narrative: The development objectives of the project are to: (a) strengthen Government of Argentina's capacity to assess and mitigate environmental risks associated with closed uranium mines, processing sites, and related mining sector investments in accordance with international good practice; and (b) reduce potential economic and health damages associated with a closed uranium mining site in Malargue, Mendoza.
